门户之见，把产业联合在一起，&ldquo;跨界&rdquo;带来跨行业的资源，以自身优势向其他行业更深处挖掘并寻求合作，&ldquo;酒香不怕巷子深&rdquo;，把瓷砖产业延伸到更多的行业中。</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 15pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21.75pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 15pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">人们生活逐渐步入快消费、高享受的节奏中，整体家居顺应了社会发展和市场需求，综合行业带来了消费便利，引领家装设计潮流。</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 15pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21.75pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 15pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">佛山瓷砖有哪些品牌开始&ldquo;跨界&rdquo;哪些品牌还未涉足？&ldquo;一加一大于二&rdquo;，适当进行营销策略调整将带来意想不到的收获。</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 15pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21.75pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 15pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 15pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">文章来源：哈德逊编辑原创</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 15pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 15pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">转载请注明出处<font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">www.hudsonhome.cn</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 15pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\